# NEST-Paket — System Map (UI + Local + API Write Layer)

## 1. Entry Points

/app/paket/page.tsx → Landing  
/app/create/page.tsx → Create (identity input)  
/app/package/page.tsx → Package (items + create handover)

---

## 2. End-to-End Flow (CREATE HANDOVER)

Landing (/paket)
→ user klik "Buat Serah Terima"
→ /create

/create
→ input sender + receiver
→ simpan draft ke localStorage
→ redirect /package

/package
→ input items + optional photo
→ POST /api/handover/create
→ clear draft
→ redirect:
   - /paket (save)
   - /handover/[id] (handover mode)

---

## 3. Package Page (/package)

File:
/app/package/page.tsx

---

### 3.1 Purpose

- Ambil draft dari localStorage
- Input daftar barang
- (optional) ambil foto
- create handover ke API

---

### 3.2 State

items: string[4]  
photoFile: File | null  
preview: string | null  
saving: boolean  

---

### 3.3 Items Logic

Initial:

["", "", "", ""]


Behavior:
- hanya items[0] wajib
- items kosong akan di-filter

Transform ke payload:

items
.filter(i => i.trim() !== "")
.map(i => ({
description: i
}))


---

### 3.4 Photo Flow

Input:
<input type="file" accept="image/*" capture="environment"> ``` id="pkg-photo-input"

Processing:

imageCompression(file, {
  maxSizeMB: 0.6,
  maxWidthOrHeight: 1600,
  useWebWorker: true
})
``` id="pkg-photo-compress"

Output:
- photoFile (compressed)
- preview (object URL)

⚠️ IMPORTANT:
- photo TIDAK dikirim ke API
- hanya disimpan di state UI

---

### 3.5 Draft Read (LocalStorage)

Keys:

draft_sender_name  
draft_receiver_name  
draft_receiver_contact  

Mapping:


sender_name
receiver_target_name
receiver_target_phone
receiver_target_email = ""


---

### 3.6 Guard (Critical)


if(!sender_name || !receiver_target_name){
alert(...)
router.push("/create")
}


Meaning:
- package page tidak bisa jalan tanpa create step
- localStorage = dependency wajib

---

### 3.7 Payload (API Contract)

POST /api/handover/create

Body:


{
sender_name: string,
receiver_target_name: string,
receiver_target_phone: string,
receiver_target_email: string,
items: [
{ description: string }
]
}


---

### 3.8 API Response (Expected)


{
success: boolean,
handover_id: string
}


---

### 3.9 Draft Cleanup

Setelah success:


removeItem:

draft_sender_name

draft_sender_contact

draft_receiver_name

draft_receiver_contact


---

### 3.10 Routing Logic

Mode:

save:
→ /paket

handover:
→ /handover/{id}

``` id="pkg-routing"

---

### 3.11 Saving Lock


if(saving) return
setSaving(true)


⚠️ Tidak di-reset kalau success  
→ karena langsung redirect

