## 8. Observed System Behavior

1. Create = hanya staging (local)
2. Package = titik commit ke DB
3. API hanya dipanggil di package
4. Photo belum masuk backend
5. Draft lifecycle jelas (write → read → delete)

---

## 9. Observed Gaps (No Assumption)

1. Photo tidak pernah dikirim ke server

→ data hilang setelah page

---

2. sender_contact tidak dipakai di payload

→ ada di draft tapi tidak dikirim

---

3. Tidak ada retry mechanism

→ jika gagal, user harus ulang manual

---

4. Tidak ada schema validation di client selain minimal check

---

5. receiver_target_email selalu kosong

---

## 10. Full Create Action Flow (Detailed)

Step-by-step:

1. User buka /paket
2. Klik "Buat Serah Terima"
3. Masuk /create
4. Input sender + receiver
5. Submit
6. Data disimpan ke localStorage
7. Redirect /package
8. Input items
9. (optional) ambil foto
10. Klik:
   - Simpan → mode save
   - Serah Terima → mode handover
11. Validasi items
12. Ambil draft dari localStorage
13. Build payload
14. POST /api/handover/create
15. Jika success:
    - hapus draft
    - redirect sesuai mode

